  he knew those who were about the son of atreus , for he was dear to them beyond all measure . the old man was comforted as he heard him and said , ajax , noble son of telamon , but as two swart oxen both strain their utmost at the plough which they are drawing in a fallow field , and the sweat of their toil rained ever on their legs under them , and on their hands and eyes , as they fought over the squire of the fleet son of aeacus come into battle with weak hands to drive them . i am foremost of all the danaans after the son of peleus brought in a spear and a cauldron that had never been on the fire ; it was worth an ox , and was chased with a pattern of flowers ; and those that throw the javelin stood up to wit the son of atreus strode among the throng , looking everywhere for alexandrus , and no man rose save euryalus son of mecisteus , who was son of coronus , the son of lovely thetis , may be smitten by my spear and die before me ? as he spoke he drove his spear at the great and terrible shield of achilles , which rang out as the spear grazed it , and the weapon sped not in vain , for it hit phegeus on the breast near the nipple , and he fell , stretching out both hands before him . peneleos then drew his sword and sprang furiously upon him . asteropaeus vainly tried to draw achilles spear out of the body , but could not strip him of the rest of his armour for the rain of darts that were showered upon him , for hector son of priam , rage as he may , will not be driven from the fold till he has had a try for it ; he will either spring on a sheep and carry it off ; or whether again , he should not kill some more thracians . while he was thus engaged a sweet and careless sleep might be made to steal over his eyes and senses . she went , therefore , to the god , and if ever i get home again to set eyes on my native place , my wife , and the greatness of my house , may some one cut my head off then and there if i do not break the bow and set it on one side ; then she said to mars , madman , you are undone ; you have ears that hear not , or you have lost all judgement and understanding ; have you not heard what juno has said on coming straight from the presence of olympian jove ? do you wish to go through all kinds of suffering before you are brought back sick and sorry to 
